| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3653 — Recovery Inhibition (alphalocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a9211dba-b2f6-5c4f-a6f9-1f7520ff1e00"
